# Claude Scaffold PRD (Single Block, Copy Ready)
name: Personal Brand Website (Richard Dillman)
version: 1.0
framework: Next.js 15
hosting: Vercel
style: TailwindCSS
content: MDX or Contentlayer
owner: Richard Dillman
authoring_agent: Claude Code

## Overview
A personal brand website that showcases engineering leadership, performance focus, and mentoring. Tone is conversational, credible, human. Goal is minimalism, clarity, speed.

## Objectives
- Present Richard as a hands on engineering leader
- Highlight performance, SEO, and architecture work
- Provide clear paths to connect
- Keep content easy to update

## Success Metrics
- LCP under 2.5s
- Lighthouse 95 plus
- Accessibility 100
- Build under 60s on Vercel

